OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FCouncillors in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,Fhave voted in favour of urging the
OL,9,FScottish Government to hold a local
OL,10,Freferendum on the proposals to create
OL,11,Fa new National Park.
OL,13,FGalloway picked as preferred site out
OL,14,Fof a shortlist of five locations, in
OL,15,FJuly 2024. Since then local public
OL,16,Fopinion has become divisive on whether
OL,17,Fplans to build the park should go
OL,18,Fahead.
