OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FA 12-week public consultation was
OL,8,Flaunched to give the local community a
OL,9,Fchance to share their views, in
OL,10,FNovember 2024.
OL,12,FCampaigners against the plans of a
OL,13,FNational Park gathered outside the
OL,14,Fcouncil's headquarters in Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway on 12 December 2024.
OL,17,FGabrielle Harrington, who's against
OL,18,Fthe plans, says the issue has created
OL,19,F"a lot of bitterness" amongst the
OL,20,Flocal community.
