OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FShe said: "There's some people in
OL,8,Ffavour, there's some against. And the
OL,9,Fonly way to solve it is a referendum,
OL,10,Feverybody has their say then, even the
OL,11,Fpeople sitting quietly at home who
OL,12,Fdon't want to be seen or heard."
OL,14,FJamie Blackett, who also gathered
OL,15,Foutside the Dumfries and Galloway
OL,16,FCouncil, says 'you cannot argue with a
OL,17,Fdemocratic vote'.
