OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FHe said: "What people will not accept
OL,8,Fis if a National Park goes ahead on
OL,9,Fthe basis of the consultations that
OL,10,Fhave gone ahead so far.
OL,12,F"There's a lot of mistrust about the
OL,13,Fwhole process and I think people think
OL,14,Fthat if a Galloway national park is to
OL,15,Fgo ahead it should be done
OL,16,Fdemocratically."
