OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FThe two national parks in Scotland are
OL,8,Fthe Cairngorms and the Loch Lomond &
OL,9,Fthe Trossachs - it has now been more
OL,10,Fthan 20 years since a new Scottish
OL,11,Farea was granted National Park status.
OL,13,FRob Lucas, from the Galloway National
OL,14,FPark Association, says the debate on a
OL,15,Fnew National Park in southern Scotland
OL,16,Fis "more complicated than a simple yes
OL,17,For no question".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
