OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,FHe said: "I think we're actually
OL,8,Fundertaking a very widespread
OL,9,Fconsultation which has gone out to
OL,10,Ffifty-two thousand households in the
OL,11,Farea. The first question being, would
OL,12,Fyou like a national park or not?
OL,14,F"That looks pretty similar to what a
OL,15,Freferendum format would be doing, so
OL,16,Fit just seems like it's asking for
OL,17,Fsomething that's already happening.
OL,19,F"Referendums are not known for
OL,20,Fbringing people together, I believe
OL,21,Fthey cause more division."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
