OL,3,CCouncillors call on Scottish
OL,4,CGovernment to hold National park
OL,5,Creferendum
OL,7,F"We will await the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment's response with interest
OL,9,Fand, in the meantime, urge the public
OL,10,Fto take part in the official
OL,11,Fconsultation process which is where
OL,12,Fthey can make their voices heard," he
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FRural Affairs Secretary Mairi Gougeon
OL,16,Fsaid: "The consultation on the
OL,17,Fproposal for a new National Park is
OL,18,Funderway and I am grateful that a date
OL,19,Fhas been set for members of the
OL,20,FCouncil to consider their response to
OL,21,Fit.
