OL,7,F"Their debate highlighted concerns
OL,8,Fabout access to paper copies of the
OL,9,Fconsultation and I would urge anyone
OL,10,Fwho wishes one to contact NatureScot
OL,11,Fand they will be sent copies.
OL,13,F"Alternatively, the full consultation
OL,14,Fsurvey is available online and all
OL,15,Fviews will be listened to and fully
OL,16,Fconsidered.
