OL,7,F"We recognise that there are differing
OL,8,Fviews, which is why it is imperative
OL,9,Fthat all those with an interest have
OL,10,Ftheir say ` including whether or not
OL,11,Fthey want a National Park in the area
OL,12,F` before the consultation closes in
OL,13,FFebruary.
