OL,7,F"Unlike a referendum, this
OL,8,Fconsultation not only asks if people
OL,9,Fwant a National Park in their area,
OL,10,Fbut also what the area, governance and
OL,11,Fpowers of a new park might be, and it
OL,12,Fallows everyone in Galloway, South and
OL,13,FEast Ayrshire and beyond the
OL,14,Fopportunity to consider the proposal
OL,15,Fand share their views."
